    <div class="about-content-wrapper">

        <p>
            Welcome to Bharati Radio, the heartbeat of our campus! Established with a vision to connect, inspire, and entertain, we are more than just a radio station—we are a vibrant community hub driven by passion. Our journey began in a small studio with big dreams, and today, we stand as the loudest voice of the students.
        </p>

